Text: 신경 쓰지 마. 다른 곳으로 가겠어.

TextEng: Err... I'll get back to you on that.
Let's fight! I'm tired of riddles!
Whoa... say all of that again.
<StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> Would you perhaps give me a hint?
Me not like riddles. Me like fighting!
Text: 나 수수께끼 싫어. 나 싸우기 좋아!

TextEng: Um... me not care for prize.
Oh, was that riddle? Me not listening.
Text: 오, 그게 수수께끼였어? 나 안 들었어.

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> Me almost get it but me need hint.
Me head hurts! Me change mind! No riddles!
Text: 나 머리 아파! 나 생각 바꿨어! 수수께끼 싫어!

TextEng: Is riddle tough? You lets me hear it?
Me not like talking. Me go now.
Me not ready to start thinking yet. Say again?
Text: 나 아직 생각할 준비 안 됐어. 다시 말해줘?

TextEng: Me think for a while. Come back, answer later.
Text: 나 좀 생각할게. 나중에 와서 대답할게.
